<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title></title>
		<style type="text/css">
			*{
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
			}
			.box1{
				width: 100px;
				height: 100px;
				background: red;
				padding: 10px;
				margin: 10px;
				border: solid 5px black;
				display: block;/*块状元素*/
			}
			.box2{
				background: blue;
			}
			span{
				width: 100px;
				height: 100px;
				background: red;
				display: inline;/*内联元素*/
				padding: 10px;
				margin: 30px;/*上下方向有问题*/
				border:solid 5px black;
			}
			img{
				width: 100px;
				padding: 10px;
				margin: 20px;
				display: inline-block;/*行内块元素*/
				background: red;
				border: solid 5px black;
			}
			.box3{
				width: 100px;
				height: 100px;
				background: green;
			}
			b{
				background: blue;
				width: 100px;
				height: 100px;
				display: none;/*隐藏*/
				/*当元素设置了float属性后，就相当于给该元素加了display:block;属性；*/
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h3>1.块状元素，特点：块状元素会按顺序自上而下排列，定义自己的宽度和高度</h3>
		<div class="box1"></div>
		<div class="box1 box2"></div>
		<h3>2.内联元素：特点：按顺序从左往右排列，不能定义它的宽和高</h3>
		<span>hello word</span>
		<span>hello word</span>
		<h3>3.行内块元素:特点：按顺序从左往右排列，定义自己的宽度和高度</h3>
		<img src="../HTML学习/img/b1.png" />
		<img src="../HTML学习/img/b1.png" />
		<b>加粗</b>
	
	</body>
</html>
